decoworld.vanilla.outside

Class ClientWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.vanilla.outside.ClientWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    decoworld.gdxmodel.RenderableWorld, decoworld.gdxmodel.SetsCamera, decoworld.gdxmodel.TakesInput, decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener, decoworld.model.world.World

    public class ClientWorld
extends java.lang.Object
implements decoworld.gdxmodel.RenderableWorld, decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener
    Represents an environment in which players can move around. This will general hold a map and some set of world items. The content that makes up the world will be provided upon instantiation; it should not be hard-coded into this class.
